						<summary>

						<p>This inscription records the gift of a village called Suviratapuram as a <hi rend="italic">dēvadāṉa</hi> to the temple of Bhānappīśvara Nayiṉār at Parittippaḷḷi-nāḍu in Kuṉṟattūrpaṟṟu surrounding Muḷvāy-in Koṅgu <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Vīraśōḻa-maṇḍalam by Viṭṭamarasar, an agent, for the merit of Narasaṇa Nāyakka Uḍaiyār.</p>						

						</summary>
